                <p><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="padding-bottom: 8px; display:block; font-size: 22px;">NATIONAL PUBLICITY OPPORTUNITY: <br />Have you coached women to break the glass ceiling?</font></p>

            	<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px; font-weight: normal;">McKinsey &amp; Co. recently released a report that said inadequate career development is holding back female executives from reaching the top ranks of the corporate ladder &ndash; and they recommend coaching and leadership training for women as the remedy. Have you successfully coached a female executive to crack the upper echelons of corporate America? If so, please send your brief story to me at <a href="mailto:amylogan@thecoaches.com" style="color: #689bbc;">amylogan@thecoaches.com</a> ASAP but not later than the end of this week, June 3. Please include your contact info and that of your client, if possible. This is for a major national Sunday newspaper career column. This will be top-tier publicity for you, your client and CTI!</p>
				
				<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px; font-weight: normal;">Thanks,<br />
				Amy</p>
				
